---
title: Bang Bang Cauliflower & Garlic Rice with Soy Veggies & Peanuts
description: Sweet with a punch of flavour that will send your tastebuds into a new dimension. We're talking about roasted cauliflower that's
been soaking up those mango chilli sauces in the oven. Drizzle with a sriracha mayo and you'll be eating with the stars tonight!
